Name: Endless Anger

Description: When the battle starts, this Axie gains 2 {Cocoon}, then its Shield cards grant 10% bonus Shield for the rest of the battle.
Name: Way of Bug

Name: Vault Builder

Name: Leech

Description: {Solo}. This Axie's Single Attacks consume 20% of the Axie's current Shield and deal bonus DMG = 3 times that amount.

Description: {Solo}. When your turn starts, this Axie gains 1 {Cocoon} then gain 5 Shield for each {Cocoon} on this Axie.

Description: {Solo}. When your turn starts in Odd <Round>, draw 1 bonus Card; in even <Round>, gain 60 Shield.

Description: This Axie deal 20% bonus DMG against enemies that have no Shield.
Name: Sharp Talon

Description: {Solo}. This Axie deals 20% bonus DMG if its HP is > 50%, and takes 20% less DMG if its HP is < 50%.

Description: {Solo}. Once per battle, if this Axie would die, it survives with 1 HP, then heals 5% of its max HP for each of its {Feather}. Afterward, deal 20 DMG to all enemies.
Name: Sacred Feather

Name: Feather Descend
